Implemented Documents View feature for displaying agent-produced reports and research. Added AgentDocument model (source, status, topic fields), loadAgentDocuments() to Store and AppViewModel, DocumentsView with filtering (source/status), search, read/unread tracking, split-pane UI with markdown rendering. Added Documents toolbar button (⌘D shortcut) with unread badge. Created comprehensive AgentDocumentsTests.swift with 13 tests covering models, filtering, search, and UI behavior. Compiles successfully; build fails only due to pre-existing Preview macro errors.